@NODE "ENGLISH"  "  Changes from V1.0xx to V1.100"

This is just the description of the changes that were made from version
V1.0xx to V1.100.

Most of them were internal changes, i.e. they do mostly not affect the
handling or look of the program. Of course, some bugs were fixed, again.

       @{"  Changes          " LINK "E-CH"}
